      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What if email worker crashes mid work?\n- Message goes back onto the queue. \n- Another worker picks it up. \n- Retried automatically.\n- User never knows. \n- Photo upload was already confirmed ✓",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What if email worker crashes mid work?\n- Message goes back onto the queue. \n- Another worker picks it up. \n- Retried automatically.\n- User never knows. \n- Photo upload was already confirmed ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
